Problem Statement

•	How to monitor and improve the efficiency of equipments like machines, stations, line? 
•	How to determine which fields are suitable for capital expansions?
Objective 

•	The above mentioned problems are faced by many firms in the manufacturing industry. Both the problems can be successfully satisfied using Overall equipment effectiveness. 

•	The tool helps the firms to calculate the overall equipment effectiveness score for the manufacturing equipments deployed by their company.

•	The tool can serve various industries which are into some or the other form of production. The overall equipment effectiveness tool helps users to keep track of the equipment’s performance and how to improve its production/effectiveness further.

•	The tool is also helpful for letting manufacturing companies make strategic capital expansion decisions by giving an idea of the production rate of their deployed equipments which in turn can be used to the advantage of investing in the equipments that perform better.
